---
title: Salmon & Lemony Charred Pea Risotto with Asparagus & Parmesan
description: Risotto’s comforting luxuriousness never fails to satisfy. With a reputation for being labor intensive—ours couldn’t be easier! This version begins with rich veggie stock, and the addition of tender, charred peas and roasted asparagus takes the dish to the next level. It’s finished with lemon zest, parsley, and a generous sprinkle of Parmesan and served with lemon and scallion greens to contrast to the risotto’s creamy richness.
